
Prerequisites
==============

the following tools are needed:

    apt-get install autoconf libtool automake autopoint pkg-config g++

the following headers are needed:

    apt-get install libjpeg62-dev libudev-dev libconfig++8-dev libjson0-dev libebml-dev libmatroska-dev libavformat-dev libccrtp-dev

for initial scan files:

    apt-get install dvb-apps


Checkout TVDaemon
==================

git clone https://github.com/neolynx/tvdaemon.git
cd tvdaemon

git submodule init
git submodule update

cd v4l-utils
git checkout master
git am ../patches/*
cd ..

# obsolete
#cd cli/cli-core
#git checkout master
#git submodule init
#git submodule update
#cd src/colorful
#git checkout master
#cd ../..
#cd ../..


Build tvdaemon
===============

cd v4l-utils
autoreconf -vfis
./configure --enable-libdvbv5
make
sudo make install
cd ..

autoreconf -vfis
./configure
make


Start tvdaemon
===============

src/tvdaemon -d -r html


GDB
====

In order to launch the application with gdb without a make install,
use libtool from the root folder: libtool --mode=execute gdb src/tvdaemon

libtool --mode=execute valgrind --leak-check=full --log-file=vg.out src/tvdaemon -d -r html

